PREHEAT oven to 350 degrees F. Lightly grease baking sheets. COMBINE flour, cocoa, baking soda and salt in small bowl. Beat butter, brown sugar and granulated sugar in large mixer bowl until light and creamy. Beat in egg and vanilla extract. COMBINE Taster's Choice and water in small bowl; stir until coffee is dissolved. Add to sugar mixture; mix well. Gradually mix in flour mixture. Stir in morsels. Drop by rounded teaspoon onto prepared baking sheets. BAKE for 10 to 12 minutes or until edges are crisp. Remove to wire racks to cool completely.